## 5. Variant A Runtime Contract Refresh (status-agnostic)

- [x] Aktualizovat `docs/status-core-plan.md` (Variant A) tak, aby definoval univerzalny runtime kontrakt (ziadne status-specific instrukcie) a aby opisoval ako maju nove statusy pouzivat `defineStatus`, `StatusTimingPhase`, pending buff pipeline a lifecycle eventy.
- [x] Vybudovat data-driven Vitest pokrytie pre cele spektrum statusov: generator cez `listStatuses()` si vyberie statusy s `spend`/`behaviorId` a spusti scenare (grant pred spendom, spend bez grantov, paralelne pending buffy, turn-limited budgety). Ziadne hardcodovanie na Chi/Evasive/Prevent Half.
- [x] Instrumentovat runtime (`setStacks`, `addStacks`, `spendStatus`, `spendStatusMany`, `applyModifiers`) aby publikoval `StatusLifecycleEvent` udalosti, ktore vie konzumovat UI, AI aj telemetry.
- [x] Rozsirit `StatusBehaviorHandlers` o nove hooky tak, aby kazdy status mohol dodat vlastnu logiku bez `if (statusId === ...)` vetiev. Behavior konfiguracia sa stane jedine miesto, kde sa riesi specificka funkcionalita.
- [x] Zjednotit logging/telemetry okolo novych eventov (Combat log, stats, `defenseDebugLog`) a zdokumentovat proces priradovania vysvetleni pre hraca.

